# Backend issues.
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Fix the TGA loader to be Endian Aware.
* Begin using 3rd Party image loaders, such as libpng.
* Models should be specified, not hardcoded.
* Texture maps should be specified not hardcoded.


